There was a boy called Peter Parker who was bitten by a radioactive spider. 
The spiders bite gave him the power to shoot webs from his hands.
His uncle ben was killed by a villain called green goblin.
He decided to use his powers to defeat green goblin.
He encounters green goblin many times but isnt able to defeat him.
He wonders who green goblin actually is.
Green goblin causes a lot of destruction to New York the city that Peter lives in.
Eventually he manages to defeat green goblin but before he does he takes off his mask.
It turns out to be his uncle.
He pushes green goblin off the building that they are on.